long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
JumpTube meaning is jump inside the video (Tube). 
Invented by Meytal Kol-Haham and Tzahi Manistersky
Activating this extension direct you to jumbtube website, viewing your embedded video and a scrolled coulomb with  text. Every line is mapped for play the video from the exact time.
